name: 1st SOLD
description:
This one is very special.

I made it to remind myself of the first one I had all editions sold.

It was like I was in a museum looking at all these paintings I made and thinking that through the NFTs I was able to take my arts to all corners of the world without even leaving my home and besides I'm getting the support of many followers and friends which has been just amazing.

Thank you very much to all those who have accompanied me here and who are supporting me.


You guys are very special to me.
